{"tid":438210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣好易暈低？","createTime":"2017-10-16T16:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T02:49:10.000Z","uid":153933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df8e9cbd88d7af102cad26fd3e8b9aed6b503d8b","tid":438210,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"成日無端端個肚攪住攪住痛<br />\n然後個頭就開始暈 開始標冷汗 睇唔到嘢<br />\n之後就成身無力暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要唔止一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有問過啲朋友 佢哋話係血糖低或者中暑<br />\n但係我成日飲珍珠奶茶、可樂e啲高糖分嘅嘢 應該唔會血糖低㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲同我一樣或者知道點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d480e7211551061bd1cce4a790338ce69f7617c8","tid":438210,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"哇，咁都唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2007da718a65599a6e817d8d3ace5d2866001cc6","tid":438210,"uid":140130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"媽媽唔好唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8deec05dd52db8c74e1c206d95fd9000bf00892","tid":438210,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇，咁都唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇過 之前暈低入左醫院check 話我好正常無事<br />\n次次都係咁"},{"pid":"ec7f210dba2267b7bebf53a17350d1dc68f827ac","tid":438210,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>媽媽唔好唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由細個已經係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個就有bb咁驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1441ee9f1994b11e7ed9821ed1d0441cea985a3e","tid":438210,"uid":102091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"血壓低都有可能"},{"pid":"9f3cf6cf4270215851f3d4bc74d2e0c90ae202b0","tid":438210,"uid":52975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"tilt table test?"},{"pid":"bf03d180322fd917208ad9baa463d1d331e19812","tid":438210,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>血壓低都有可能</blockquote><br />\n但醫院check過血壓 又話我無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed7845d5e7c0ec5d013d6590b09a0dc47d341f2","tid":438210,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"肚邊個位痛？<br />\n有冇伴隨噁心嘔吐？"},{"pid":"a2be405851cf6b63cac8ba913de7f476499e8501","tid":438210,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數都係朝早企得耐開始眼花胃痛想嘔 發面白晒出冷汗 有時手腳會痺<br />\n但有次係坐左成個鐘之後肚痛眼花暈<br />\n通常發作開始之後坐十分鐘無事<br />\n不過未試過暈低<br />\n去過醫院驗左血都係話無事"},{"pid":"4ca83acd60226bd292ab52e13b7436f7aa8aa878","tid":438210,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"我細個都係咁<br />\n但我第一下唔係肚痛，我係突然呼吸困難 然後就同你講嘅差唔多"},{"pid":"5f83cfdacd86f0f7df6244aab22b45d15196bfae","tid":438210,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16